      <title>拜登拨款 6200 万美元帮助加速氢能应用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/biden-awards-62-million-to-help-speed-hydrogen-adoption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府将拨款 6200 万美元，用于加速该国新兴的氢能产业的发展，该产业被视为实现钢铁、水泥和重型运输脱碳的关键。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/biden-awards-62-million-to-help-speed-hydrogen-adoption</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
