      <title>加州立法者通过法案，要求对奴隶制道歉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/california-lawmakers-pass-bill-requiring-apology-for-slavery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州立法者通过了一项法案，要求对奴隶制持续造成的危害进行正式道歉，奴隶制虽然不合法，但在 1850 年加州建州后却得到容忍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/california-lawmakers-pass-bill-requiring-apology-for-slavery</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 13:12:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
